name: Cozy Jungle Print Baby Romper
description: Bring comfort and cuteness together with our Cozy Jungle Print Baby Romper! Made from soft, breathable fabric, this adorable romper keeps your little one cozy while they crawl, play, and explore. The cheerful jungle animal print featuring lions, elephants, giraffes, and more adds a playful touch.  Available in sizes for 6-9 Months & 9-12 months, this romper is the perfect blend of comfort, style, and practicality. A must-have for your baby's wardrobe or a thoughtful gift for new parents.
